ons are not being met in practice as the interests of smallholder farmers are poorly addressed.REDD+ policy developers and implementers need more focus on understanding the interests and dynamics of smallholder agriculturalists to enable inclusive, realistic and long-lasting projects.For REDD+ to succeed, funders need to consider how to better ensure long-term livelihood security for farming communities.
