ld be raised. In addition, depending on the "mutual substitution effect " between different conditions, to achieve the same improvement in rural areas with a low level of "social capital ", the focus should be on improving the "trustworthiness of village leaders ". For rural areas with a slight difference in "household income level ", the focus should be on promoting the formation of "environmentally friendly habits " among rural residents.
